'''普通夜鹰'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Caprimulgus indicus''}}），俗稱'''蚊母'''、'''吐蚊鳥'''或'''貼樹皮'''，古稱'''{{ruby-py|鷏|-{zh-cn:tián;zh-tw:ㄊㄧㄢˊ}-}}'''，为[[夜鹰科|夜鹰科]][[夜鹰属|夜鹰属]]的[[鸟类|鸟类]]。该物种的模式产地在[[印度|印度]]。<ref name='id2249'/>

==描述==
[[File:CaprimulgusIndicus1.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:2005-grey-nightjar-with-chick.jpg|thumb]]

普通夜鷹身長為21-24cm，其斯里蘭卡亞種（英文名稱：kelaarti）體型較小。普通夜鷹身體大部分為灰色，在冠上有黑色條紋，在其翅上沒有紅褐色的、鮮艷的斑點。其尾呈灰色，帶有分開的黑色窄條紋。雄性在頸部中間位置間有白色斑點，雌性頸部有紅褐色斑點和“submoustachial”色的條紋。普通夜鷹通常的叫聲為“thacoo”或“chuck”（均爲英文擬聲詞，下同），它們通常以每兩秒五次的頻率重複上述叫聲。<ref>{{cite book|author=Whistler, Hugh|year=1949|edition=4th| title=Popular handbook of Indian birds|url=https://archive.org/stream/popularhandbooko033226mbp#page/n367/mode/2up|page=317| publisher=Gurney and Jackson|place=London}}</ref>
如同在遠處傳來的引擎聲。<ref name=navarro>{{cite journal|author= Navarro, A |year=1976| title= Some observations on the breeding habits of the Indian Jungle Nightjar ''Caprimulgus indicus indicus'' in Khandala|journal=[[Newsletter_for_Birdwatchers|Newsletter for Birdwatchers]] | volume=16|issue=3|pages=3–4|url=https://archive.org/stream/NLBW16#page/n32/mode/1up}}</ref><ref name="#1">{{cite journal| author=Phillips, WWA| year=1949| title=Nightjars| journal=J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.| volume=48| issue=2| pages=359–361| url=https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/48731847| access-date=2018-09-03| archive-date=2020-02-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202052217/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/48731847| dead-url=no}}</ref>

除此之外普通夜鷹還會“唱歌”，歌聲由“FWik-m”組成，通常舒緩而又有槼律，如此重複十秒。這樣的“歌聲”有時會以急促的“foo-foo”聲（如同向著一個空瓶瓶口吹氣一般）結尾。另外，一種被描述爲是普通夜鷹的“uk-krukroo”聲由Ali and Ripley記載，但這種聲音其實是[[东方角鸮|东方角鸮]]的叫聲<ref name=pcr>{{cite journal|author1=Rasmussen, PC  |author2=JC Anderton |year= 2005| title= Birds of South Asia: The Ripley Guide. Volume 2|publisher= Smithsonian Institution & Lynx Edicions|page=251}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Blanford, WT|year=1895|title=Fauna of British India. Birds. Volume 3|url=https://archive.org/stream/faunaofbritishin03oate#page/190/mode/2up|pages=190–191| publisher=Taylor and Francis|place=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/stream/BakerFbiBirds4/BakerFBI4#page/n396/mode/1up|pages=366–379|title=Fauna of British India. Birds. Volume 4|edition=2nd|author=Baker, ECS| year=1927|publisher= Taylor and Francis| place= London}}</ref>

==分类==
[[File:Jungle_nigthjar_Chikmagalur.jpg|thumb]]

印度和斯里蘭卡種群包含于普通夜鷹，但是jotaka（外文名）由於其卵的顔色和叫聲與普通夜鷹不同，所以單獨分爲一物種：[[日本夜鷹|日本夜鷹]]，此分類由Rasmussen和Anderton于2015年完成。在喜馬拉雅地區、西從哈扎拉到不丹，南到孟加拉國發現的叫做“hazarae”，隨後被分爲[[日本夜鷹|日本夜鷹]]的亞種“Caprimulgus jotaka”。
<ref name=pcr>{{cite journal|author1=Rasmussen, PC  |author2=JC Anderton |year= 2005| title= Birds of South Asia: The Ripley Guide. Volume 2|publisher= Smithsonian Institution & Lynx Edicions|page=251}}</ref> 
有關“jotaka”的研究記錄來源於Andamans和Phuentsholing <ref>{{cite journal|author=Abdulali, Humayun|year=1970|title=An addition to the list of Indian birds - the migratory Jungle Nightjar, ''Caprimulgus indicus jotaka'' Temm. & Schl.|journal=J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=67|issue=2|pages=331–332|url=https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/47819905|access-date=2018-09-03|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202052211/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/47819905|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite journal|author1=Abdulali, Humayun|author2=Hussain,SA|year=1971|title=A second record of the migratory Jungle Nightjar (''Caprimulgus indicus jotaka'' Temm. & Schl.) in Indian limits|journal=J. Bombay Nat. Hist. Soc.|volume=68|issue=2|pages=451–452|url=https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/48430639|access-date=2018-09-03|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202052213/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/48430639|dead-url=no}}</ref>
早期的研究報告包括廣汎分佈在（中國和日本的）有遷徙的亞種“jotaka”和“phalaena”
<ref>{{cite book|title=Check-list of birds of the world. Volume 4|author=Peters, JL|year=1940|publisher=Harvard University Press|place=Cambridge, Massachusetts|pages=203–204|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/14476674|access-date=2018-09-03|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202052151/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/14476674|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
其[[二名法|二名法]]名字的含義是“來自印度的夜鷹（{{Lang-en|nightjar from India}}）”，這樣有時會與“C. asiaticus”混淆，後者是{{Tsl|en|Indian_nightjar|Indian nightjar}}，爲了將兩者分清，早些時候的“C. indicus”名字叫做“large Indian nightjar”。

==行爲==
普通夜鷹在黃昏時變得活躍，通常會在丘陵或灌木叢之上，會有规律地挑一個自己最喜歡的突出、裸露的杆子或石頭栖息。普通夜鷹也会樹林中休息，例如在樹枝上縱向休憩。
<ref name=navarro>{{cite journal|author= Navarro, A |year=1976| title= Some observations on the breeding habits of the Indian Jungle Nightjar ''Caprimulgus indicus indicus'' in Khandala|journal=[[Newsletter_for_Birdwatchers|Newsletter for Birdwatchers]] | volume=16|issue=3|pages=3–4|url=https://archive.org/stream/NLBW16#page/n32/mode/1up}}</ref><ref name="#1"/> 

在印度生活的普通夜鷹交配季節為一月至六月；位於斯里蘭卡的是三月至七月。它們的窩即爲在地上一個裸露的坑，雌性會在其中產卵。<ref name=pcr/><ref>{{cite book|author=Hume, AO|year=1890|title=The nests and eggs of Indian Birds. Volume 3|edition=2nd|pages=40–43|url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/16925535|publisher=R. H. Porter|place=London|access-date=2018-09-04|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202052147/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/16925535|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
雌性與雄性都會參與孵卵，大約持續16至17天。<ref name=hbk>{{cite book|author1=Ali, S  |author2=S D Ripley| title=Handbook of the Birds of India and Pakistan. Volume 4|edition=2nd|year=1983|publisher=Oxford University Press|place= New Delhi|pages=8–12}}</ref>

